text.section:
Neither a nonparticipating manufacturer nor a brand family shall be included or retained in the directory if the Attorney General determines that:
Any escrow payment required pursuant to KRS 131.602 for any period for any brand family, whether or not listed by the nonparticipating manufacturer, has not been fully paid into a qualified escrow fund governed by a qualified escrow agreement that has been approved by the Attorney General;
Any outstanding final judgment, including interest thereon, for a violation of KRS 131.602 has not been fully satisfied for the brand family or the manufacturer;
The requirements for certification under KRS 131.608 have not been met; or
The financial instrument required by KRS 131.602(10) has not been posted.
